'''quartile''' (''plural'' '''quartiles''')

#{{statistics}} Any of the three [[point]]s that divide an [[ordered]] [[distribution]] into four parts, each containing a [[quarter]] of the [[population]].
#{{statistics}} Any one of the four groups so divided.
